{
  "video_id": "WKmsxJkJCqM",
  "title": "Should schoolchildren have jobs? 6 Minute English",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6460.0,
      "end_time": 9260.0,
      "text": "Neil: Hello and welcome to 6 Minute English. I'm Neil"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9460.0,
      "end_time": 12840.0,
      "text": "and joining me today is Dan who is a producer at BBC"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12840.0,
      "end_time": 14680.0,
      "text": "Learning English - that's his job."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 15200.0,
      "end_time": 19400.0,
      "text": "Dan: Hi everyone... Yes that is my job, obviously"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 19420.0,
      "end_time": 21420.0,
      "text": "- why are we discussing that now, Neil?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 21840.0,
      "end_time": 23780.0,
      "text": "Neil: Well you haven't always been a producer"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 23960.0,
      "end_time": 25360.0,
      "text": "at BBC Learning English, have you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25540.0,
      "end_time": 27419.0,
      "text": "Dan: No... I used to be a teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 27660.0,
      "end_time": 31280.0,
      "text": "Neil: And before that? Way back - your first ever job?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31280.0,
      "end_time": 34200.0,
      "text": "Dan: Ah, I had a paper round when I was 14."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34440.0,
      "end_time": 37440.0,
      "text": "A paper round is a job - the job of delivering"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37560.0,
      "end_time": 39460.0,
      "text": "newspapers to people's homes."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39460.0,
      "end_time": 41660.0,
      "text": "It's often done by teenagers."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41860.0,
      "end_time": 44240.0,
      "text": "Neil: 14 seems very young to be at work."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44780.0,
      "end_time": 46780.0,
      "text": "And that's the topic of this 6 Minute English:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47200.0,
      "end_time": 48920.0,
      "text": "Should schoolchildren have jobs?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 49300.0,
      "end_time": 51779.0,
      "text": "It seems fewer and fewer have these days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51860.0,
      "end_time": 55190.0,
      "text": "according to the statistics. We'll give you 6 words"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55140.0,
      "end_time": 57460.0,
      "text": "and expressions - and, of course, our quiz question."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57460.0,
      "end_time": 58360.0,
      "text": "You Ready?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 58360.0,
      "end_time": 59320.0,
      "text": "Dan: You bet!"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59600.0,
      "end_time": 61980.0,
      "text": "Neil: What is the youngest age at which children"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 62600.0,
      "end_time": 68400.0,
      "text": "are allowed to work in the UK? Is it a) 12, b) 13, c) 14"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68720.0,
      "end_time": 71760.0,
      "text": "Dan: Well, I'm going to say 14 just because that's"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71880.0,
      "end_time": 75000.0,
      "text": "how old I was and it seems such a long time ago!"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75200.0,
      "end_time": 77740.0,
      "text": "Neil: We'll find out if you're right or wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77900.0,
      "end_time": 78940.0,
      "text": "at the end of the programme."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78940.0,
      "end_time": 81860.0,
      "text": "Let's start by hearing some British teenagers"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82600.0,
      "end_time": 84000.0,
      "text": "talking about their Saturday jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 87440.0,
      "text": "Dan: A Saturday job is the name we give to part-time"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87440.0,
      "end_time": 90520.0,
      "text": "work that teenagers do for extra money."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90720.0,
      "end_time": 93460.0,
      "text": "As the name suggests, these jobs often"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 93460.0,
      "end_time": 96919.0,
      "text": "take place on Saturdays - but not always."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 97600.0,
      "end_time": 99580.0,
      "text": "Neil: That's right - 'Saturday job' is general term"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 99820.0,
      "end_time": 103800.0,
      "text": "we use to describe part-time work done by teenagers."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103460.0,
      "end_time": 105259.0,
      "text": "The work might take place on Sundays"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105480.0,
      "end_time": 108100.0,
      "text": "or any day of the week, in fact! Let's hear from"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108140.0,
      "end_time": 110740.0,
      "text": "these British children about their Saturday jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111220.0,
      "end_time": 113380.0,
      "text": "Insert Vox: We have to face all the stuff on the shelves"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 113380.0,
      "end_time": 115839.0,
      "text": "and make it look organised and show customers"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 115840.0,
      "end_time": 117680.0,
      "text": "where products are if they need to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 117680.0,
      "end_time": 119860.0,
      "text": "On the average week I work nine hours, so"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 120200.0,
      "end_time": 122280.0,
      "text": "two hours for two school nights and then I work"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 122380.0,
      "end_time": 124820.0,
      "text": "four hours on a Saturday and two hours on a Sunday."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 124820.0,
      "end_time": 127380.0,
      "text": "And then in the school holidays I can work more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127500.0,
      "end_time": 130840.0,
      "text": "so it's like around 16 in the school holidays"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 131500.0,
      "end_time": 134600.0,
      "text": "Dan: The first teenager said the work involves"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 134600.0,
      "end_time": 136640.0,
      "text": "making the shelves look organised."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 136900.0,
      "end_time": 139740.0,
      "text": "Shop work is a very typical Saturday job."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 139740.0,
      "end_time": 142140.0,
      "text": "Neil: Oh yes, I spent many a weekend and evening"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 142340.0,
      "end_time": 145340.0,
      "text": "stacking shelves! The second teenager's Saturday job"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 145520.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "takes place Saturdays, Sundays and evenings."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 148560.0,
      "end_time": 151660.0,
      "text": "As we said - A Saturday job's not just for Saturdays."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 151920.0,
      "end_time": 155220.0,
      "text": "Dan: A Saturday job is seen almost as a rite of passage"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 155220.0,
      "end_time": 158520.0,
      "text": "in the UK. A rite of passage is the name we give"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 158660.0,
      "end_time": 162600.0,
      "text": "to events or ceremonies that form an important stage"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 162600.0,
      "end_time": 163660.0,
      "text": "in a person's life."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 163660.0,
      "end_time": 165520.0,
      "text": "Neil: That's right - like graduating from school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 165580.0,
      "end_time": 168320.0,
      "text": "or having children. But according to the latest"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 168400.0,
      "end_time": 171460.0,
      "text": "statistics in the UK, that is all changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 172200.0,
      "end_time": 173440.0,
      "text": "Listen to this BBC report."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 174800.0,
      "end_time": 175940.0,
      "text": "BBC reporter: In order to work, they need a permit"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 175940.0,
      "end_time": 178300.0,
      "text": "from the local authority and our data shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 178460.0,
      "end_time": 180920.0,
      "text": "the number being issued has fallen"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 180920.0,
      "end_time": 184339.0,
      "text": "from nearly 30,000 permits in 2012"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 184780.0,
      "end_time": 188100.0,
      "text": "to just 23,000 in 2016."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 188380.0,
      "end_time": 191100.0,
      "text": "Employers frequently bemoan the lack of work"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 191100.0,
      "end_time": 192900.0,
      "text": "experience young people have."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 193120.0,
      "end_time": 196280.0,
      "text": "But teenagers are also facing pressure not to take up"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 196420.0,
      "end_time": 198559.0,
      "text": "part-time jobs and to concentrate"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 198680.0,
      "end_time": 200640.0,
      "text": "on their studies instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 201200.0,
      "end_time": 204500.0,
      "text": "Dan: So, it seems that fewer teenagers are taking"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 204720.0,
      "end_time": 207820.0,
      "text": "Saturday jobs. But there's a conflict here."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 208400.0,
      "end_time": 210400.0,
      "text": "Neil: Yes, on the one hand, employers bemoan"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 210600.0,
      "end_time": 213400.0,
      "text": "the lack of work experience young people have."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 213320.0,
      "end_time": 215120.0,
      "text": "Bemoan, meaning complain about."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 215120.0,
      "end_time": 217120.0,
      "text": "It's a rather formal word."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 217380.0,
      "end_time": 219920.0,
      "text": "Dan: But on the other hand, teenagers are facing"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 220240.0,
      "end_time": 222640.0,
      "text": "pressure not to take part-time jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 222800.0,
      "end_time": 224980.0,
      "text": "and to concentrate on their studies."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 225440.0,
      "end_time": 228320.0,
      "text": "Some people think working could be detrimental"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 228600.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "to a schoolchild's academic progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 231560.0,
      "end_time": 234460.0,
      "text": "Neil: Detrimental - which means causing harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 234680.0,
      "end_time": 237400.0,
      "text": "It's a tricky one, isn't it? I think my Saturdays"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 237220.0,
      "end_time": 239540.0,
      "text": "spend stacking shelves and serving fish 'n' chips"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 239540.0,
      "end_time": 241540.0,
      "text": "taught me valuable lessons about working"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 241640.0,
      "end_time": 244179.0,
      "text": "with adults and also managing my money."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 244580.0,
      "end_time": 247000.0,
      "text": "I don't think it was detrimental to my education."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 247300.0,
      "end_time": 248980.0,
      "text": "Dan: Well, you managed to get a job at BBC"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 249100.0,
      "end_time": 249600.0,
      "text": "Learning English!"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 249600.0,
      "end_time": 250540.0,
      "text": "Neil: That's true."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 250800.0,
      "end_time": 253320.0,
      "text": "Dan: As for me, my paper round taught me the value"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 253460.0,
      "end_time": 258790.0,
      "text": "of hard work. It didn't hinder me. Hinder means to stop"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 258240.0,
      "end_time": 260519.0,
      "text": "someone or something from making progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 260839.0,
      "end_time": 263359.0,
      "text": "Neil: Well let's not talk too much in case we hinder"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 263360.0,
      "end_time": 267000.0,
      "text": "our students... On to the answer to our quiz question."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 267340.0,
      "end_time": 270979.0,
      "text": "I asked this: What is the youngest age at which children"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 271100.0,
      "end_time": 272700.0,
      "text": "are allowed to work in the UK?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 272860.0,
      "end_time": 276300.0,
      "text": "Is it a) 12, b) 13 c) 14"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 276640.0,
      "end_time": 278460.0,
      "text": "Dan: I said c) 14."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 278700.0,
      "end_time": 280520.0,
      "text": "Neil: And I'm afraid you are wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 281540.0,
      "end_time": 284360.0,
      "text": "You are allowed to work from the age of 13 in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 284560.0,
      "end_time": 286660.0,
      "text": "Exceptions to this rule include TV,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 286660.0,
      "end_time": 287560.0,
      "text": "theatre and modelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 287800.0,
      "end_time": 289540.0,
      "text": "Dan: Oh well - I guess I should have spent"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 289640.0,
      "end_time": 290740.0,
      "text": "more time at school."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 290940.0,
      "end_time": 292920.0,
      "text": "Neil: Shall we have a recap of the vocabulary?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 293240.0,
      "end_time": 295360.0,
      "text": "Dan: Did you have a paper round as a kid, Neil?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 295600.0,
      "end_time": 298700.0,
      "text": "Neil: No I didn't, but I did help my best friend James"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 298820.0,
      "end_time": 301520.0,
      "text": "deliver newspapers - in return for a pound."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 301780.0,
      "end_time": 302760.0,
      "text": "Big money back in the 80s!"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 303320.0,
      "end_time": 304719.0,
      "text": "Dan: Did you supplement your earnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 304800.0,
      "end_time": 306800.0,
      "text": "with a Saturday job?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 306260.0,
      "end_time": 308760.0,
      "text": "Neil: I did. I had a Saturday job in a supermarket"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 308760.0,
      "end_time": 310820.0,
      "text": "and also in a fish 'n' chip shop - but it"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 311000.0,
      "end_time": 312580.0,
      "text": "wasn't always on a Saturday."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 313100.0,
      "end_time": 315400.0,
      "text": "Dan is that a wedding ring on your finger?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 315240.0,
      "end_time": 318380.0,
      "text": "Dan: Yes it is. Marriage is a rite of passage"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 318380.0,
      "end_time": 321000.0,
      "text": "in many cultures. It is an important stage"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 321000.0,
      "end_time": 324100.0,
      "text": "in a person's life - talking of which, are those your"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 324160.0,
      "end_time": 325380.0,
      "text": "kids on your screensaver?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 325620.0,
      "end_time": 327900.0,
      "text": "Neil: Yep - having children is another example"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 328400.0,
      "end_time": 331520.0,
      "text": "of a rite of passage. See how tired I look!"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 331780.0,
      "end_time": 334580.0,
      "text": "Dan: Do not bemoan your lack of sleep! I'm sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 334760.0,
      "end_time": 338280.0,
      "text": "they're wonderful people. Bemoan's a quite formal way"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 338280.0,
      "end_time": 339679.0,
      "text": "of saying 'complain about'."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 340120.0,
      "end_time": 342360.0,
      "text": "Neil: I think it's OK to bemoan a lack of sleep"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 342360.0,
      "end_time": 344980.0,
      "text": "- it can have a detrimental effect on my health."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 345200.0,
      "end_time": 347979.0,
      "text": "Dan: Detrimental - meaning harmful."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 347980.0,
      "end_time": 350720.0,
      "text": "As long as your tiredness doesn't hinder your work"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 350720.0,
      "end_time": 351760.0,
      "text": "on 6 Minute English"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 352180.0,
      "end_time": 355600.0,
      "text": "Neil: Well, I'd never let anything hinder my work"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 355160.0,
      "end_time": 356240.0,
      "text": "on 6 Minute English -"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 356240.0,
      "end_time": 358860.0,
      "text": "that means stop from making progress."
    },
    {
